{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T06:18:20.671Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the official Claude Code documentation, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"What Is the Agent SDK\""},{"type":"text","text":" refers to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"the Claude Agent SDK (formerly Claude Code SDK)"},{"type":"text","text":" — a development library that exposes Claude Code's core capabilities as programmable tools, enabling you to build production AI agents that autonomously read files, run commands, search the web, edit code, and perform complex development workflows."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Core Definition"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Agent SDK is Claude Code as a library"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude Code (CLI) → Agent SDK (library)\n    ↓\nSame tools, agent loop, and context management\n    ↓\nProgrammable in Python and TypeScript"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key renaming"},{"type":"text","text":": \"The Claude Code SDK has been renamed to the Claude Agent SDK\"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Enables"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"AI Agent Capabilities"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Build AI agents that can:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Capability"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Read files"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Access and analyze codebase files"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Run commands"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Execute shell commands, scripts"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Search the web"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Browse for information, research"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Edit code"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Modify source files, create new code"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Autonomous workflows"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Build their own context, decide trajectories, work autonomously"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"What it does"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Give you the same tools, agent loop, and context management that power Claude Code, programmable in Python and TypeScript\"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Features"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Built-in Tools"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Agent SDK includes built-in tools for:\n- reading files\n- running commands\n- editing code"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefit"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Your agent can start working immediately without you implementing tool execution\"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. The Agent Loop (Core Architecture)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Four-step loop"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Gather Context → Agent reads files, runs commands to understand situation\n2. Take Action → Agent decides what to do (edit code, run commands)\n3. Verify Work → Agent checks if action succeeded\n4. Repeat → Loop until task complete"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Definition"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Agents are systems that build their own context, decide their own trajectories, and work very autonomously\"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. Harness (Agent Infrastructure)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A robust agent requires more than just a model — it needs a "},{"type":"te